data.title: Bad old seafood , shrimp is old and the oisters are raw and bad taste
data.text: Well we whent to day to this disgusthing place it should be close for good and not sell bad raw seafood , I order a Bomba it have shrimps , octopus and oisters bad choice I did I mean I hope I wont go to the emergency room tonite becouse of this toxic bad seafood is scary how can you get sick fast by eating bad seafood . By the way they took to long just to give us bad food and this was to go ok and I didnt like the place is dirty and loud music bad spencive food attitudes,  my suggestion is not to go to this supposed to seafood restaurant is prety bad and by the way they dont put the phone number on the recipe so you wont call them and tell how horrible your food is . data.title: great resturant food is awesome
data.text: great customer service in the restaurant its an all sea food menu it has a live bad every weekend there is some wait since its becoming so popular but its doesn't take more than 20 minutes usually but they are expanding to a patio area so hopefully wait time will be less I recommend going with out children on the weekends so you can enjoy the music
